<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ChatLock - LockModes</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">

<!-- Main Container -->
<div class="container mx-auto p-8">

    <!-- Title Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-600">🔐 1. LockModes – Post Control Jaise Pehle Kabhi Nahi</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">ChatLock mein har post, story, ya blip ke saath ek special feature milta hai jiska naam hai LockMode.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-500">🛡️ LockMode kya karta hai?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Ye feature content creators ko apne content ke upar <strong>full control</strong> deta hai — kaun dekh sakta hai, kab tak dekh sakta hai, aur kaise access kar sakta hai.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 - Set Exact Visibility -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600">1. Set Exact Visibility (Kaun dekh sakta hai)</h2>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Close Friends Only</strong>: Sirf aapke selected close friends ko dikhai degi post.</li>
            <li><strong>Mutuals</strong>: Sirf wo log dekh sakte hain jo aapko follow karte hain aur aap bhi unhe follow karte ho.</li>
            <li><strong>Anonymous Followers</strong>: Aise followers jinke naam ya profile details aapko nahi dikhte, unko bhi visibility set kar sakte ho.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3 - Auto-Lock After Time -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600">2. Auto-Lock After Time (Samay ke baad automatic lock hona)</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Aap apni post ya story ko aise set kar sakte ho ki wo kuch samay baad <strong>khud hi lock</strong> ho jaye, jaise ek "timed vault".</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Example: Aap post karte ho aur set karte ho ki 3 ghante baad ye sirf mujhe hi visible rahe, ya 24 ghante ke baad post automatically lock ho jaye.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4 - Unlockable Posts -->
    <div class="mb-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600">3. Unlockable Posts (Request karke access lena)</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Kuch posts ko aap <strong>Unlockable</strong> bana sakte ho. Jab koi user aisi post dekhna chahega, to usse ek <strong>custom message</strong> bhejna padega request karne ke liye.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Aap decide karoge ki request accept karni hai ya nahi. Ye feature khas taur pe kaam ka hai:</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Artists</strong> apne premium art work ko limited audience ke saath share kar sakte hain.</li>
            <li><strong>Creators</strong> apne exclusive content ko sirf un logon ko dikhate hain jo real interest dikhate hain.</li>
            <li><strong>Private Sharing</strong> ke liye bhi perfect hai — jaise close family ya ek special circle ke saath koi yaadgar moment share karna.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 5 - Example Section -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600">🔥 Samjho ek Real-Life Example:</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Rahul</strong> ek photographer hai. Usne apne kuch personal art photos daale ChatLock pe. Wo chahta hai ki sirf close friends ya serious art lovers unhe dekhe.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">To Rahul ne LockMode set kiya:</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc text-gray-700 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Close Friends Only</strong> ke liye ek album.</li>
            <li>Kuch special photos <strong>Unlockable</strong> rakhe — jo log unlock request bhejenge aur jab Rahul approve karega tabhi dekh sakenge.</li>
            <li>Aur kuch photos ko set kiya auto-lock hone ke liye 6 ghante baad, taki bas ek limited time tak available rahein.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Final Section -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
